Installation:

	git clone git://github.com/wangzq/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Load submodules:

  cd ~/.vim
  git submodule init
  git submodule update

Example: add a new submodule

  cd ~/.vim
  git submodule add http://github.com/tpope/vim-fugitive.git bundle/fugitive
  git add .
  git commit -m "Install fugitive"
  git push


